result.title: New max and min number of registrants
result.content:
In Codeforces contest(Rockethon 2015 ) there were x6565 registrants, which is new max number of registrants and min number of registrants in Codeforces Alpha Round #20 (Codeforces format) there were x60.

And the site didn't go down during the contest, well done Codeforces team. :)
